original_title: The Dark at the End of the Tunnel
overview: Girl goes jogging in the woods but all is not what it seems in this student-made horror short film created in 2 days with a two person crew. Filmed with a Black Magic Ursa Mini 4k at 24fps starring Bethany Stone, Hannah Verdi, and Trisha Braun.
title: The Dark at the End of the Tunnel
